\par }{\fs22 He smiled back at her}{\fs22\lang2057 .\rquote }{\fs22 Jump in, then.  Let\rquote s go for a test ride.  See if it\rquote s true love or just infatuation.\rquote   He glanced around the street quickly.  None of the
