\par }{\fs22 \lquote I\rquote m a hundred for full service, sweetie,\rquote  she said as she wiggled her tight little butt inside the Jag.  Her perfume smelled like eau de bubble gum and she seemed to have bathed in it.}{\fs24 
\par }{\fs22\lang2057 \lquote }{\fs22 As I said, get into the car.  A hundred dollars is petty cash for me.\rquote }{\fs24 
\par }{\fs22 He knew he shouldn\rquote t be picking her up in the Jaguar, but he took her for a joy ride anyway.  He couldn\rquote t help himself now.}{\fs24 
\par }{\fs22 He brought the girl to a small wooded park in a part of Washington called Shaw.  He parked in a thicket of fir trees that hid the car from sight.  He looked at the prostitute and she was even smaller and younger than he had thought.}{\fs24 
\par }{\fs22 \lquote How old are you?\rquote  he asked.}{\fs24 
\par }{\fs22 \lquote How old you want me to be?\rquote  she said and smiled.  \lquote Sweetheart, I need the money first.  You know how it works.\rquote }{\fs24 
\par }{\fs22 \lquote Yes.  But do you?\rquote  he asked.}{\fs24 
\par }{\fs22 He reached into his pocket, and pulled out a switchblade knife.  He had it at her throat in an instant.}{\fs24 
\par }{\fs22 \lquote Don\rquote t hurt me,\rquote  She whispered.  \lquote Just be cool.\rquote }{\fs24 
\par }{\fs22 \lquote Get out of the car.  Slowly.  Don\rquote t you dare scream.  You be}{\b\fs22  }{\fs22 cool.\rquote }{\fs24 
\par }{\fs22 Shafer got out with her, staying close, the knife still pressed to the hollow of her throat.}{\fs24 
\par }{\fs22 This is a fantasy game}{\fs22\lang2057 ,\rquote }{\fs22  he explained.  \lquote It\rquote s all just a game, darling.  I play with three other men - in England, Jamaica, and Thailand.  
Their names are Famine, War, and Conqueror.  My name is Death.  You\rquote re a very lucky girl \endash }{\fs22\lang2057 I\rquote m}{\i\fs22  }{\fs22 the best player of all.\rquote }{\fs24 
