\par I had been waiting a long time to be in love again, but this was wor
th it and then some.  I grabbed hold of Christine as soon as we were inside her house.  My hands began to trace her waist, her hips; they played over her breasts, her shoulders, then touched the delicate bones of her face.  We liked to do this slowly, no 
need to rush.  I kissed her lips, then gently scratched her back and shoulders.  I pulled her closer, closer.
\par \lquote You have the gentlest touch,\rquote  she whispered against my cheek.  \lquote I could do this all night.  Be just like this.  You want some wine?  Anything?  I\rquote ll give you anything I have.\rquote 
\par \lquote I love you,\rquote  I told her, still lightly scratching her lower back.  \lquote We will do this forever.  I have no doubt of it.\rquote 
\par \lquote I love you so much.\rquote   she whispered, then I heard her breath softly catch.  \lquote So please, try to be careful, Alex.  At work.\rquote 
\par \lquote Okay, I will.  But not tonight,\rquote   I said.
\par Christine smiled.  \lquote Not tonight.  Tonight you can live dangerously.  We both will.  You are handsome, and debonair for a policeman.\rquote 
\par \lquote Or even for an international jewel thief.\rquote 
\par I swept her up and carried her down the hallway to the bedroom.  \lquote Mmm.  Strong, too.\rquote   she said.  She flicked on a hall lamp as we passed.  It was just enough light to see where we were going.
\par \lquote How about a trip somewhere?\rquote   I said.  \lquote I need to get away.\rquote 
\par \lquote That sounds good.  Yes - before school starts.  Anywhere.  Take me away from all this.\rquote 
\par Her room smelled of fresh flowers.  There were pink and red roses on the nightstand.  She has a passion for flowers and gardening.
\par \lquote You planned this all along, didn\rquote t you?\rquote   I said.  \lquote You did.  This is entrapment.  You sly girl.\rquote 
\par \lquote I was thinking about it all day.\rquote   she confessed and sighed contentedly.  \lquote I thought about being with you all day, in my office, in the hallways, the schoolyard, and then in my car on the way to the restaurant.  I\rquote 
ve been having erotic day-dreams about you all day.\rquote 
\par \lquote I hope I can live up to them.\rquote 
\par \lquote You will.  No doubt about it.\rquote 
\par I took off her black silk blouse in one sweeping motion.  I put my mouth to a breast, pulling at it through her demi bra.  She was wearing a brushed leather skirt and I didn\rquote 
t take it off, just slowly pushed it up.  I knelt and kissed her ankles, the tops of her feet, then slowly came up her long legs.  She massaged my neck, my back and shoulders.
\par \lquote You are dangerous tonight,\rquote  she said.  \lquote That\rquote s a good thing.\rquote 
\par \lquote Sexual healing.\rquote 
\par \lquote Mmm, please.  Heal me all over, Doctor.\rquote 
\par She bit down hard into my shoulder, then even harder into the side of my neck.  We were both breathing fast.  She moved against me then opened her legs for me.  I moved inside
 her.  She felt incredibly warm.  The bed-springs began to sing and the headboard rocked into the wall.
\par She pushed her hair to one side, behind an ear.  I love the way she does that.
\par \lquote You feel so good Oh, Alex, don\rquote t stop, don\rquote t stop, don\rquote t stop,\rquote  she whispered.
\par I did as I was told and I loved every moment, every movement we made together, and I even wondered for a second if we had made a baby.
