\par Everybody was calling me \lquote sugar\rquote , following Sampson\rquote s lead.  The \lquote love\rquote  word was used, and overused.  I was roasted and toasted in sent
imental speeches that seemed hilarious at the time.  Just about everybody had too much to drink.
