ar East, Bangkok, the Philippines, Malaysia.  Women abducted and murdered - all Jane Does.  To be honest, nothing too promising at this point.\rquote 
\par I imagined him pursing his thin lips and nodding thoughtfully.  \lquote I understand, Alex.  Please keep giving me whatever you get from your sources.  It\rquote 
s difficult for us to get help outside this small island.  My calls for assistance frequently aren\rquote t returned.  I sincerely wish that I had some good news for you on my end, but I\rquote m afraid I don\rquote t.\rquote 
