\par \lquote Police business.\rquote   I gave him a hard stare.  \lquote Take a walk, please.  Go!\rquote 
\par \lquote Don\rquote t look like no police business to me,\rquote  he mumbled.
\par The man moved away, looking over his shoulder as he retreated down Fourth, frowning, but not stopping to argue with me.
