\par \lquote This is Alex Cross.\rquote   I said.
\par \lquote Yes, I know who you are.  That\rquote s already been established.  Here\rquote s what you should do.  Back all the way off.  Just back away.  Before you lose everything you care about.  It can happen so easily.  In a snap.  You\rquote 
re smart enough to understand that, aren\rquote t you?\rquote 
