\par \lquote The Wizards kicked butt,\rquote  Damon said with a straight face.  \lquote Rod Strickland had a double-double.\rquote 
\par \lquote Shhhh.\rquote   Nana gave us both a mighty look of irritation.  \lquote CNN 
